---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import presentationImg from '../assets/images/Presentazione.jpeg';
import Sfondo1 from '../assets/images/Sfondo1.png';
---

<section id="presentation" class="py-20 bg-black">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center -mx-4">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 px-4 mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <Image 
          src={presentationImg} 
          alt="Locandina Presentazione Soul 'N Da Hole"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl border-2 border-[color:var(--card-border)] hover:border-[color:var(--gold)] transition-all duration-300"
          width={720}
        />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 px-4 text-center md:text-left">
        <div class="section-heading mb-8">
          <span class="sh-label inline-block text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[color:var(--gold-dim)]" style="opacity:0; font-family: var(--font-label);">Evento</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase text-white mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-display); text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.18); overflow:hidden;">
            <span class="reveal-line inline-block" style="transform: translateY(105%);">Evento di Lancio</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="sh-desc text-lg text-gray-300" style="opacity:0;">
            Unisciti a noi per la presentazione ufficiale del torneo e scopri in anteprima squadre, programma e sorprese.
          </p>
          <div class="gold-rule mt-6 flex items-center gap-3 justify-center md:justify-start">
            <div class="gr-line" style="flex:1; height:1px; background:var(--gold-dim); transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:center;"></div>
            <span class="gr-star" style="color:var(--gold); font-size:.7rem; opacity:0;">✦</span>
            <div class="gr-line" style="flex:1; height:1px; background:var(--gold-dim); transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:center;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Unisciti a noi per la presentazione ufficiale del torneo Soul 'N Da Hole.
          Scopri in anteprima le squadre, il programma e tutte le sorprese che abbiamo in serbo.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
          <div class="info-box bg-[color:var(--card-bg)] border border-[color:var(--card-border)] rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-white">29.06.2025</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Data</p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-box bg-[color:var(--card-bg)] border border-[color:var(--card-border)] rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-white">19:00</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Ora</p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-box bg-[color:var(--card-bg)] border border-[color:var(--card-border)] rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-white">'La Torre'</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400">San Vincenzo (LI)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .info-box {
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .info-box:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
</style>
